Android is finally fighting back against scammers with new security features in version 16. Linus recently collaborated with Kitboga to see just how aggressive and manipulative scam tactics can get, and the experience was both ridiculous and unsettling. With new tools like AI-driven scam detection, call-based sideloading restrictions, and screen sharing warnings, Google is making a serious push to protect users. Linus and Luke discuss.
